summary:
Realistic player castle/keep on lake klinalth in Falkreath hold.
Based on historical norman keeps. Matching interior and exterior.
descriptionHtml:
Realistic player castle/keep on lake klinalth in Falkreath hold.
Based on historical norman keeps. Matching interior and exterior.

Features:
*Two interior cells the keep and the guard barracks
*The keep has all the space you need;
-Kitchen
-Diningroom
-Bedroom
-Alchemy room
-Enchanting room
-Libary
-Weapon and armor display
*4 Followers 3 guards and 1 blacksmith
*Working drawbridge and portcullis
*Custom made stairtower
*Completly navmeshed
*Fast travel
*Horse fast travel (Horse will be placed in the stable)

NOTE!Â 
This is nog some big palace complex but a keep/castle based on true historical norman keeps. That being said it has al the space and crafting facilities you need.

Only needs Skyrim.esm
